A somehow MVC architecture must be placed or starts taking place to allow the script to extend in a modular way without getting a spaghetti nested code that will be a challenge to decipher.

Creating Folder "core" to have the core PHP classes.
Creating folder "libs" to have all external PHP frameworks/libs from 3rd party open source projects
